Keitumetse Bridgette Tlhomelang (amụrụ na 28 Disemba 1975) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa nke na-eje ozi dị ka onye African National Congress Member of Parliament si North West
Tlhomelang bụ onye otu African National Congress

Ọ nọ n'ọnọdụ nke asatọ na ndepụta ANC nke ndị omeiwu si North West maka ntuli aka ndị omeiwu nke Mee 8, 2019. ANC meriri 63.69% nke ngụkọta vootu na vootu mba na mpaghara ahụ, na-enye ya ohere itoolu n'ime oche mpaghara iri na atọ na National Assembly, ụlọ nke ala nke ndị omeiwu. A họpụtara Tlhomelang ka ọ bụrụ onye omebe iwu nke mba ahụ ma ṅụọ iyi n'oge nnọkọ mbụ nke National Assembly mgbe ntuli aka ahụ gasịrị na 22 Mee 2019.

A họpụtara Tlhomelang ka ọ rụọ ọrụ na Kọmitii Portfolio na Small Business Development maka Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu nke isii (20192024) na 27 June 2019. N'abalị iri na abụọ n'ọnwa Julaị, a họpụtara ya ka ọ rụọ ọrụ na Kọmitii Na-eduzi nke nwere mmadụ ise nke Multi-Party Women's Caucus.
